<HEADLINE> Macao UNESCO Center Inaugurated </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, June 29 (Xinhua) -- The Macao UNESCO Center was
inaugurated on Monday, aiming to promote Macao's education,
science and culture levels and enhance its relations with the U.N.
body.
</P>
<P>
Established with the support from UNESCO's Bangkok branch, the
center has a library, an exhibition hall and an auditorium for
meetings and seminars.
</P>
<P>
