education, science and culture, he said.
</P>
<P>
Macao became a quasi-member of UNESCO in October 1995 thanks to
the great efforts by the Chinese and Portuguese governments, he
said. Macao attended the biennial UNESCO meeting in 1997 which was
held in UNESCO headquarters in Paris. 
