<HEADLINE> U.S. President Clinton Arrives in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 29 (Xinhua) -- U.S. President Bill Clinton
and Mrs. Clinton arrived in Shanghai this evening to continue his
nine-day state visit to China.
</P>
<P>
