<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Index Up 6.22 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
BANGKOK, June 29 (Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of Thailand
(SET) index Monday gained 6.22 points from last Friday to close at
271.20.
</P>
<P>
Some 109 million shares worth 1.09 billion baht (26.5 million
U.S. dollars) changed hands Monday.
</P>
<P>
The SET index last Friday gained 0.89 points from Thursday to
close at 264.98. 
