better for the benefit of the people of the two countries," he
said.
</P>
<P>
Speaking on behalf of the Tanzania-Cuba Friendship
Association, Salim Msoma, a permanent secretary in the Tanzanian
Ministry of Communication and Transport, paid tribute to the
Cuban government for its tireless efforts in assisting Tanzanians
in various fields.
</P>
<P>
Entralgo is going to be replaced by Claudio Garcia, who also
attended the party with his wife at the Russian-Tanzanian
Cultural Center in the city.
