<P>
The gamblers were detained late Thursday during the
Mexico-Netherlands match, a police spokesman of Ho Chi Minh City
said.
</P>
<P>
Police seized close to 130 million dong (10,000 U.S. dollars)
and 10 mobile phones and arrested both owners of the cafe and 29
patrons. 
</P>
