<HEADLINE> Monday's Fixtures at World Cup Finals </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
PARIS, June 28 (Xinhua) -- Following are Monday's fixtures at
World Cup finals (all in GMT time):
</P>
<P>
At Montpellier:
</P>
<P>
Germany vs Mexico, at 14:30
